snippet.title: Final Destination Bloodlines | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Death is a relentless son of a *****. #FinalDestination #Bloodlines - Only in Theaters and IMAX May 16. #FilmedforIMAX

The newest chapter in New Line Cinema‚Äôs bloody successful franchise takes audiences back to the very beginning of Death‚Äôs twisted sense of justice‚Äî‚ÄúFinal Destination Bloodlines.‚Äù  

Plagued by a violent recurring nightmare, college student Stefanie heads home to track down the one person who might be able to break the cycle and save her family from the grisly demise that inevitably awaits them all. 
‚ÄúFinal Destination Bloodlines‚Äù stars Kaitlyn Santa Juana, Teo Briones, Richard Harmon, Owen Patrick Joyner, Anna Lore, with Brec Bassinger, and Tony Todd.

The film is directed by Adam Stein & Zach Lipovsky. The screenplay is by Guy Busick & Lori Evans Taylor, and story is by Jon Watts and Guy Busick & Lori Evans Taylor. It is based on characters created by Jeffrey Reddick.
‚ÄúFinal Destination Bloodlines‚Äù is produced by Craig Perry, Sheila Hanahan Taylor, Jon Watts, Dianne McGunigle and Toby Emmerich. The executive producers are David Siegel and Warren Zide. The behind-the-camera talent includes director of photography Christian Sebaldt and production designer Rachel O‚ÄôToole. The film is edited by Sabrina Pitre. The music is by Tim Wynn. The costumes are designed by Michelle Hunter. The casting is by Rich Delia.

New Line Cinema presents A Practical Pictures / Freshman Year / Fireside Films Production: ‚ÄúFinal Destination Bloodlines.‚Äù The film will be distributed in theaters and IMAX worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures, in theaters only nationwide on May 16, 2025, and internationally beginning on 14 May 2025.

snippet.title: Coke Studio Bharat | HOLO LOLO | Shankuraj Konwar X Shalmali Kholgade
snippet.description:
Across cultures, resilience and wisdom are often passed down through generations, shaping how we navigate adulthood. Inspired by the famed Moran community, #HoloLolo is a soulful track performed by Assam local #shankurajkonwar, as he tells the story of the challenges of navigating adulthood along with #shalmalikholgade, who brings her unique perspective. A variety of cultural instruments - namely the toka, gogona, and siphung, play an integral role in the composition, bringing alive the sounds of Assam, elevated with supporting electronic soundscapes.

Listen to HOLO LOLO - http://umgindia.lnk.to/HoloLolo

localized.title: Coke Studio Bharat | HOLO LOLO | Shankuraj Konwar X Shalmali Kholgade
localized.description:
Across cultures, resilience and wisdom are often passed down through generations, shaping how we navigate adulthood. Inspired by the famed Moran community, #HoloLolo is a soulful track performed by Assam local #shankurajkonwar, as he tells the story of the challenges of navigating adulthood along with #shalmalikholgade, who brings her unique perspective. A variety of cultural instruments - namely the toka, gogona, and siphung, play an integral role in the composition, bringing alive the sounds of Assam, elevated with supporting electronic soundscapes.

Listen to HOLO LOLO - http://umgindia.lnk.to/HoloLolo

*CREDITS*

Composer: Shankuraj Konwar
Singers: Shankuraj Konwar, Shalmali Kholgade

Aas Paas is a story of love, sacrifice, and the struggles within the relationships we often take for granted.

snippet.title: Exploring the World's Largest Cave (Hidden for 3 Million Years)
snippet.description:
Thank you, Opera, for sponsoring this video! Upgrade your browsing experience with Opera:  https://opr.as/03-Opera-browser-ruhicenetvideos
If you want to learn more about Son Doong or visit Son Doong, you can check Oxalis's website:  https://www.oxalisadventure.com

Son Doong, the largest cave on our planet. This cave is so massive that it has a completely self-sustaining ecosystem with its own climate conditions. Hundreds of meters underground, the clouds you're used to seeing in the sky form inside this cave. 

Son Doong even has an untouched prehistoric rainforest hidden far below the surface and a vast underground river. From transparent fish to colorful monkeys, over 250 endemic plant and animal species live in this underground world. Seven new animal species were recently discovered here and are unique to this place. Stretching 9 kilometers in length, this cave holds 38.5 million cubic meters of space. And its passages are so enormous that a 40-story skyscraper could fit inside and its giant stalagmites are rising like the towers of ancient cities. Walking inside, it‚Äôs impossible not to feel as small as a tiny bug. Son Doong even contains phytokarst rocks, which move towards the sun like semi-living organisms. Rare cave pearls and many other unique formations are also found here.

For 3 million years since its formation, the world had no idea about this cave's existence until it was fully explored in 2009 in Vietnam. Now, it‚Äôs time for you to see the largest cave on earth. 
Individual access is forbidden to protect both visitors and the fragile environment. This expedition is operated by Oxalis, the only authorized agency.

Note: This video contains a paid promotion! Also, the flooding footage between 2:09 and 2:13 are shot by Ryan Deboodt.
Subscribe to our channel from here ‚ñ∫ https://goo.gl/MKi8tn
"Rediscovery" Series ‚ñ∫ https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL40Eh9f0PRRXcCkyKxrtRvE3tbmcKYvHr

Visiting the World's Hottest Place (70¬∞C, 159¬∞F) LUT DESERT ‚ñ∫ https://youtu.be/NhyDkHaUC8U
Visiting the World‚Äôs Most Da–øge–≥ous Road: ‚ÄúKarakoram D‚ÑÆath Road‚Äù (There are casuaIti‚ÑÆs!) ‚ñ∫ https://youtu.be/FryCzL17YRs
Visiting the MOST AIR POLLUTED CITY in the World (Dust Hell) ‚ñ∫ https://youtu.be/zC4saZg6sG0
Visiting the COLDEST CITY in the World (-71¬∞C, -96¬∞F) YAKUTSK / YAKUTIA ‚ñ∫ https://youtu.be/Fz4ZMLsPzqM
8 Crazy Experiments at -55¬∞C, -67¬∞F (The coldest city in the World: Yakutsk) ‚ñ∫ https://youtu.be/ExoOL2lwlWE
World's Poorest Country "Burundi" (I can‚Äôt forget the things I saw) ‚ñ∫ https://youtu.be/n0gFsHf9cIw

My name is Ruhi √áenet, I'm an independent documentary maker. I go to unique places or meet unique people and investigate or analyze them with a unique approach. My motto is "curiosity is the best guide". Join me, let's learn something different...

id.title: 100 Jam Dalam Gua Terbesar di Dunia (Tersembunyi Selama 3 Juta Tahun)
id.description:
Anda dapat mengunduh Opera dari sini ‚ñ∫ https://opr.as/03-Opera-browser-ruhicenetvideos
Jika Anda ingin mempelajari lebih lanjut tentang Son Doong atau mengunjungi Son Doong, Anda dapat memeriksa situs web Oxalis ‚ñ∫ https://www.oxalisadventure.com

Son Doong, gua terbesar di planet kita. Gua ini sangat besar sehingga memiliki ekosistem yang sepenuhnya mandiri dengan kondisi iklimnya sendiri. Ratusan meter di bawah tanah, awan yang biasa Anda lihat di langit terbentuk di dalam gua ini.

Son Doong bahkan memiliki hutan hujan prasejarah yang belum tersentuh yang tersembunyi jauh di bawah permukaan dan sungai bawah tanah yang luas. Dari ikan transparan hingga monyet berwarna-warni, lebih dari 250 spesies tumbuhan dan hewan endemik hidup di dunia bawah tanah ini. Tujuh spesies hewan baru baru-baru ini ditemukan di sini dan merupakan spesies unik di tempat ini. Membentang sepanjang 9 kilometer, gua ini menampung 38,5 juta meter kubik ruang. Dan lorong-lorongnya begitu besar sehingga gedung pencakar langit setinggi 40 lantai dapat masuk ke dalamnya dan stalagmitnya yang raksasa menjulang tinggi seperti menara-menara kota kuno. Berjalan di dalamnya, mustahil untuk tidak merasa sekecil serangga kecil. Son Doong bahkan mengandung batuan fitokarst, yang bergerak ke arah matahari seperti organisme setengah hidup. Mutiara gua yang langka dan banyak formasi unik lainnya juga ditemukan di sini.

Selama 3 juta tahun sejak terbentuknya, dunia tidak mengetahui keberadaan gua ini hingga akhirnya dieksplorasi sepenuhnya pada tahun 2009 di Vietnam. Sekarang, saatnya bagi Anda untuk melihat gua terbesar di bumi ini.

Akses individu dilarang untuk melindungi pengunjung dan lingkungan yang rapuh. Ekspedisi ini dioperasikan oleh Oxalis, satu-satunya badan resmi.

Aas Paas Episode 24 - [Eng Sub] - Laiba Khan - Ali Ansari - 25th March 2025 - HAR PAL GEO

Aas Paas is a story of love, sacrifice, and the struggles within the relationships we often take for granted.
Arshia, a strong-willed young woman, is determined to reunite her broken family after her father abandons them. Meanwhile, Dr. Saham, a dedicated professional carrying his own burdens,
crosses paths with her.
Bound by their selflessness, they embark on a journey where their devotion to family is tested, and their own happiness is put on the line.
Will Arshia succeed in bringing her family back together? What challenges await Dr. Saham and Arshia? Could love blossom between them?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Director: Muhammad Iftikhar Iffi
Writer: Samra Bukhari

snippet.description:

Presenting the first single ''Prema Velluva'' from ''HIT 3'' starring Nani and Srinidhi Shetty. Directed by Dr. Sailesh Kolanu. Music Composed by Mickey J Meyer. Sung by Sid Sriram and Nutana Mohan. 

Song Credits:
Singers: Sid Sriram, Nutana Mohan
Lyrics: Krishna Kanth
Music: Mickey J Meyer
Choreography: Vishwa Raghu
Costume Designer: Nani Kamarsu
Stills: Sridhar Chadalawada
Keyboards: Mickey J Meyer
Rhythm: Venkatesh Patvari
Bass: Neil
Song Mixed by: Mickey J Meyer
Song Mastered by: Darren Vermaas (NY)
Music Recording Studio: Inspire Studio (California, Hyderabad)

Cast & Crew Details:
Starring 'Natural Star' as 'Arjun Sarkaar'.
Writer & Director : Dr. Sailesh Kolanu
Producer : Prashanti Tipirneni
Banners : Wall Poster Cinema & Unanimous Productions
Music : Mickey J Meyer

Production Designer : Sri Nagendra Tangala
Executive Producer : S Venkatratnam (Venkat)

PRO : Vamsi Shekar
Marketing : First Show
Publicity Designs : Aesthetic Kunjamma

Lyrics:

Dhuke naapai ila 
Ivvale ye ye 
Prema velluvaa

Pallavi 1:
Pagale naa vaipuki nadiche kalavaa 
Paduthuu yegire alavaa
Manase ninu chudani okate godava 
Kanule ipude chadhivaa
Venta vacchave Vembadinchaave 
Oopiralle maarave nede neeve
Nammi theerale kala kaadhe 
Peruke nenunnale praanam neeve
Yevarevarani vethikina Kanulaki thanu dhorikenaa 
Marichaanika dheninainaa nee valana
 
Pallavi 2:
Telusa tholisaariga 
Manase gelichaa 
Yepudu yedhute nilichaa
Kopam marichaanugaa Idi nee mahimaa?
Nijame nuvu naa sagamaa?

okatokatiga cherenaa

snippet.title: Train -The Unforgettable Journey | Stand up Comedy By Harsh Gujral
snippet.description:
This video is a satirical take on incidents that even Men have to go through in our day to day lives. I have tried to convey a simple message that Men's Safety is never been talked about in this country but deserves equal attention and solutions. Train The Unforgettable Journey has all my experiences and problems i have faced while travelling in a public transport in a funny manner. Please watch the video share with your friends so that there is a message spread in a funny way.
Thank You.

About CID:
-----------------
The first thrilling investigative series on Indian Television is today one of the most popular shows on Sony Entertainment Television. Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces with non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman [played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam]. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. At every stage, the plot throws up intriguing twists and turns to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.

About CID:
-----------------
The first thrilling investigative series on Indian Television is today one of the most popular shows on Sony Entertainment Television. Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces with non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman [played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam]. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. At every stage, the plot throws up intriguing twists and turns to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.

Show Synopsis : Four brave female police officers of Aminabad police station use their wittiness and emotional intelligence to tackle the various challenges they face at their work. The head of the pack is S.H.O Haseena Mallik, witty, romantic leads by example. The common challenge for all these women is to bring sensitivity to their policing while dealing with cases that come to this police station. Hence their solution are mostly unusual. The characters and the cases add to the fun and humour of the show. While Pushpa and Karishma are the saas bahu duo, who keep us entertained by their Squabbles, it is Haseena - Karishma's ideological differences which add to the drama and comedy.

snippet.title: NEW! Ep 4354 - Bagha aur Nattu kaka ki Jhuth Padegi Mehengi?!| Taarak Mehta ka Ooltah Chashmah
snippet.description:
Gokuldham Society | Gada Electronics

Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Sachin Shroff / Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta
Sunayana Fozdar / Neha Mehta as Anjali Taarak Mehta
Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide
Sonalika Joshi as Madhvi Aatmaram Bhide
Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani / Khushi Mali as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder Suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi
Kavi Kumar Azad / Nirmal Soni as Dr. Hansraj Hathi 
Ambika Ranjankar as Komal Hansraj Hathi

Shyam Pathak as Popatlal Pandey

Tanmay Vekaria as Bagha

snippet.title: Sikandar Main Villain - Salman Khan vs Aamir Khan | Deeksha Sharma
snippet.description:
Sikandar Trailer Surprised everyone with last 30 Seconds, Director AR Murugadoss Hinting towards Ghajini level Emotions & Rashmika Mandanna Character already leading to Shocking Climax. But here comes Aamir Khan Cameo which might change everything, Is it Really Ghajini vs Sikandar on 30 March or AR Murugadoss is cooking something really big this time?

Sikandar Trailer Breakdown & Full Movie Prediction with Surprise Cameos would be shared in this Video. 

Sikandar is an upcoming Indian Hindi-language romantic action thriller film directed by A. R. Murugadoss and produced by Sajid Nadiadwala. The film stars Salman Khan in the titular role, alongside Rashmika Mandanna, Kajal Aggarwal, Sathyaraj, Sharman Joshi, and Prateik Babbar.

The film was officially announced on 10 April 2024. Principal photography commenced the following June in Mumbai and wrapped by March 2025. The film has songs composed by Pritam, background score composed by Santhosh Narayanan, cinematography handled by Tirru and editing by Vivek Harshan. With an estimated production budget of ‚Çπ200 crore, it is one of the most expensive Indian films of all time.

Vela vela vennelantha
Meedha vaali velugunantha
Moyamante nenu entha.. Arere‚Ä¶
Chinni gunde unnadhentha
Haayi nimpi gaalinantha
Oodhamante oopirentha.. Arere‚Ä¶
Kallu rendu pusthakaalu
Bhasha leni aksharaalu
Choopulone ardhamayye.. Anni maatalu‚Ä¶
Mundhu leni aanavaalu
Leniponi kaaranaalu
Kotha kotha onamaalu.. Enni maayalu‚Ä¶
Kathalenno cheppaaru
Kavithalni raasaaru
Kaalaalu dhaataaru
Yuddhaalu chesaaru
Premalo.. Thappu ledhu premalo.. || 2 ||
Charanam 1:
Aakaasham thaakaali ani undha
Naatho raa chupisthaa aa saradhaa
Nelanthaa chuttese veelundhaa
Emundhi premisthe saripodhaa
Aha mabbulanni kommalai
Poolavaana pampithe
Aa vaana peru prema le
Dhaani ooru manamu le
Ye manasuni yemadagaku ye rujuvini.. Oh.. Anthe.. Oh..
|| Kathalenno ||
Charanam 2:
Enthunte entantaa dhooraalu
Rekkallaa ayipothe paadhaalu
Unnaayaa bandhinche dhaaraalu
Oohallo untunte praanaalu
Are ningi loni chukkale
Kindhakochi cherithe
Avi neeku edhuru nilipithe
Undipova ikkade
Jaabili itu cherenu porapaatuna ani.. Oh.. Inthe.. Oh..
|| Kathalenno ||
